name: Empowered Dark Caster
description: This item does 35% more damage to all monsters and gives 25% more gold/exp/rep/cp when equipped. Sought after for ages, the Dark Caster finally emerges to celebrate the Dark Lord's 21,000th birthday. Although there are many followers who claim to be a part of the Undead Legion, Dark Casters are unmistakably the most dedicated and commend.
